OL,14,Gwinning BBC Radio 4 series The
OL,15,GInfinite Monkey Cage with Professor
OL,16,GBrian Cox. As a stand up Robin has
OL,17,Gtoured the world and as an author he
OL,18,Ghas written four acclaimed books,
OL,19,Gincluding Bibliomaniac, which earned
OL,20,Ghim the prestigious Booksellers
